            "content": [
              {
                "data": {},
                "content": [
                  {
                    "data": {},
                    "marks": [],
                    "value": "I've always wanted to build a game. I've also never known how.",
                    "nodeType": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "nodeType": "paragraph"
              },
              {
                "data": {},
                "content": [
                  {
                    "data": {},
                    "marks": [],
                    "value": "But I do know how to build React Apps, so why not start there?",
                    "nodeType": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "nodeType": "paragraph"
              },
              {
                "data": {},
                "content": [
                  {
                    "data": {},
                    "marks": [],
                    "value": "Hermes is my attempt at creating a working \"game\" with React. It's still an on-going project, but it's got a decent amount of features in a small package.",
                    "nodeType": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "nodeType": "paragraph"
              },
              {
                "data": {},
                "content": [
                  {
                    "data": {},
                    "marks": [],
                    "value": "The inspiration for the game comes from Eve Online, an MMORPG set in space.",
                    "nodeType": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "nodeType": "paragraph"
              },
              {
                "data": {},
                "content": [
                  {
                    "data": {},
                    "marks": [],
                    "value": "In Hermes, the user controls the ship to travel to distant planets, buying and selling items to gain money required to upgrade the ship.",
                    "nodeType": "text"
                  }
                ],
                "nodeType": "paragraph"
              },
              {
                "data": {
